  <div>
    <p>
      Dust is a Javascript templating engine. It inherits its look from the ctemplate family of languages, 
      and is designed to run asynchronously on both the server and the browser.
    </p>
  </div>
{/section1}

{<section2 }
  <div>
    <p>
